{
  "stem": "11998.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They didn't have a camp doctor in that town, so they brought the sick people, they brought to Sosnoweic and they wanted to replace them with other healthier people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And while this was in process, my father escaped from that transport coming back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he hid out and then, eventually, he came home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And after that he was hiding out, and he actually became like-- [NON-ENGLISH] caught him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The police-- we had Jewish police at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they found out where he is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they came to my mother, and they said, either he gives himself up, or we catch him and we're going to send him back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "If he gives himself up and if he agrees to become a policeman, then he can stay in the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a very difficult choice for him to make.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time the police were not involved in any of the deportations or anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were mainly traffic cops.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my father joined the police force and his duties were mainly those of keeping traffic and making sure that there's is no disturbances and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were already in a sort of enclosed area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then in 1942-- in the spring of 1942-- the whole town was ordered to go to a place-- a park.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A huge park.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the kids of course, we were thinking this was a picnic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, by that time, we already worked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we thought there was a day off from work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a marvelous day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a beautiful, sunny May day.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
